snippet.title: Limit Theory Gameplay Demo 3
snippet.description: Demonstration of an early prototype of the tactical interface, an intuitive way to issue fleet commands in Limit Theory. Learn more at http://LTheory.com. Support the dream at http://kickstarter.LTheory.com !
